text: "57 Channels (And Nothin' On)" is a 1992 song by Bruce Springsteen. It is the second single from his ninth studio album Human Touch and went to number 68 in the United States, number 32 in the United Kingdom and Sweden, number 39 in the Netherlands, number 9 in Sweden and number 25 in Canada. The music video was made for the single. ==References== Category:1992 songs Category:Bruce Springsteen songs
